## Asking the right question

Researched had been done on several case of floods in Malaysia which narrow down this project to find out which rivers in state of Selangor is at high risk to cause flood during raining.

## Finding & Getting Data

The data of water river level and rain fall retrieve from Department of Irrigation and Drainage Malaysia website. This involved process of data acquisition and merging set of data from multiple rivers to become one data set.
http://infobanjir.water.gov.my/

</style>

## Data Cleaning & Processing

Missing data from certain rivers due to malfunction sensor is remove from the data set. Attribute in the data is identified and classified accordingly. Finally the data transform into csv format for analysis.


